title: UpdateStar Premium Edition v11.0 build 1297
description:
UpdateStar Premium Edition v11.0 build 1297

Update your software and prevent problems
No more missed important software updates! UpdateStar 11 lets you stay up to date and secure with the software on your computer.

Stay up to date and secure with your software
Secure and verified downloads without advertising
Protects against outdated software on your computer!
Enhance your "Add or Remove Programs" experience
Personalize your updates
